## When to Think of Two Pointers?

### Arrays
- Sorted array
- Pair sum
- Triplet sum
- Quadruplet sum
- Remove duplicates
- Remove elements
- Merge sorted arrays
- Target sum problems

### Linked Lists
- Detect cycle
- Find middle node
- Find kth node from end
- Palindrome linked list

