# Pattern 4: Remove Duplicates

### Condition
- Sorted Array

```java
int slow = 0;

for(int fast = 1; fast < n; fast++) {

    if(arr[fast] != arr[slow]) {

        slow++;
        arr[slow] = arr[fast];
    }
}
```

### Complexity

```text
Time  : O(n)
Space : O(1)
```

---

# Pattern 5: Remove Specific Element

```java
int slow = 0;

for(int fast = 0; fast < n; fast++) {

    if(arr[fast] != key) {

        arr[slow] = arr[fast];
        slow++;
    }
}
```

### Complexity

```text
Time  : O(n)
Space : O(1)
```

