# Pattern 6: Merge Sorted Arrays

### Condition
- Two Sorted Arrays

```java
int i = 0;
int j = 0;

while(i < n1 && j < n2) {

    if(a[i] <= b[j]) {
        i++;
    } else {
        j++;
    }
}
```

### Complexity

```text
Time  : O(n + m)
Space : O(1)
```

