# Pattern 7: Detect Cycle in Linked List

### Floyd Cycle Detection

```java
ListNode slow = head;
ListNode fast = head;

while(fast != null && fast.next != null) {

    slow = slow.next;
    fast = fast.next.next;

    if(slow == fast)
        return true;
}
```

### Complexity

```text
Time  : O(n)
Space : O(1)
```

---

# Pattern 8: Find Middle Node

```java
ListNode slow = head;
ListNode fast = head;

while(fast != null && fast.next != null) {

    slow = slow.next;
    fast = fast.next.next;
}

return slow;
```

### Complexity

```text
Time  : O(n)
Space : O(1)
```

---

# Pattern 9: Palindrome Linked List

### Steps

```text
1. Find middle node
2. Reverse second half
3. Compare both halves
```

Uses:

```java
slow
fast
```

### Complexity

```text
Time  : O(n)
Space : O(1)
```

